Customer Feedback

In order to properly investigate and respond to your feedback, we ask that you write to us. We may not have all the information available at our fingertips and we would prefer to get it in writing to make sure that there have been no misunderstandings.

Once we receive your written feedback we will respond back to you, please allow at least 15 business days for this to occur. If you do not require a response, we also welcome any feedback and suggestions on how we might improve our services.

Please submit your feedback using our online Customer Care Feedback Form.

If you are unable to access the above form please mail a typed letter with a detailed description of your case to one of the addresses listed below. To assist us with our investigation of your experience, please ensure that you include as much as you can from the following information in your description:

  • Booking reference number (displayed in the upper right corner of your itinerary)
  • Full name, address and contact phone number(s).
  • Flight origin and destination.
  • Flight date and time.

Compassionate Requests

If you or a passenger you are travelling with is unable to travel due to the passing away or illness of a passenger or immediate family member, you may wish to make a compassionate request.

Unless otherwise stated, bookings are non-refundable and limited changes are permitted, charges apply. However, at our discretion we may be able to offer you some additional options for your booking.

For more information and to submit a request online please use our Compassionate Request Form.
